ontribution to the DM relic density from direct and cascade\ndecays of the inflaton. Finally, we consider the case of a gravitino as dark\nmatter. We find strong bounds from overclosure and Big Bang Nucleosynthesis,\nand derive lower limits on $T_R$ which depend on the gravitino mass and on the\nnature of the lightest ordinary superpartner.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 May 2014 20:43:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Oct 2014 20:21:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
