vel of corruption is\nthus allowed in the quantization process, up to the appearance of a systematic\nbias in the reconstruction error of (almost) consistent signal estimates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 May 2014 21:44:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2015 12:16:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 20 Apr 2016 08:15:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-21"}
