aracterization of functions preserving positivity in\nall dimensions obtained by Schoenberg and Rudin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 May 2014 02:00:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Jun 2015 23:41:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 15 Sep 2015 14:31:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2017 17:55:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-08"}
