e EDM are far in excess of what\naccelerators will be able to probe. The sensitivity of the EDM to CP phases\nboth in the SUSY and the non-SUSY sectors are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 31 May 2014 15:23:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Aug 2014 20:29:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
